title: Lockdown Logic Rears Its Head in Stock Rally Running on Nerves
description: (Bloomberg) -- When banks started going belly up, positioning in bonds turned on a dime. Forget inflation. The country is spiraling toward a recession. Yields plunged, higher interest rates were priced out.
